            "title": "Bat Flies of the Family Streblidae (Diptera: Hippoboscoidea) Host Relatives of Medically and Agriculturally Important “Bat-Associated” Viruses",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "María M.",
                    "lastName": "Ramírez-Martínez"
                },
                {
